      ],
      "inputs": [
        {
          "key": "in",
          "label": "In",
          "type": "flow"
        }
      ],
      "outputs": [
        {
          "key": "out",
          "label": "Out",
          "type": "content"
        }
      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Focus Scoped Authority\n\nKeep one shared node collection, but move execution authority with navigation focus. Reload should act on the focused fragment only, in place.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "isRoot": true,
        "root": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "focus-auth-structure",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Shared Structure",
      "position": {
        "x": -140,
        "y": -40
      },
      "width": 360,
      "height": 210,
      "color": "#00897b",
      "ports": [
        {
          "id": "in",
          "label": "In",
          "direction": "input",
          "dataType": "flow",
          "position": {
            "side": "left",
            "offset": 0.5
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "out",
          "label": "Out",
          "direction": "output",
          "dataType": "content",
          "position": {
            "side": "right",
            "offset": 0.5
          }
        }
      ],
      "inputs": [
        {
          "key": "in",
          "label": "In",
          "type": "flow"
        }
      ],
      "outputs": [
        {
          "key": "out",
          "label": "Out",
          "type": "content"
        }
      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Shared Structure\n\n- All loaded nodes coexist in one runtime collection.\n- Graph sections stay where they were authored.\n- Navigation does not move graph features around.\n- Every materialized node carries fragment provenance.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "isRoot": false,
        "root": false
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "focus-auth-exec",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Focus-Scoped Execution",
      "position": {
        "x": 320,
        "y": -40
      },
      "width": 360,
      "height": 210,
      "color": "#8e24aa",
      "ports": [
        {
          "id": "in",
          "label": "In",
          "direction": "input",
          "dataType": "flow",
          "position": {
            "side": "left",
            "offset": 0.5
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "out",
          "label": "Out",
          "direction": "output",
          "dataType": "content",
          "position": {
            "side": "right",
            "offset": 0.5
          }
        }
      ],
      "inputs": [
        {
          "key": "in",
          "label": "In",
          "type": "flow"
        }
      ],
      "outputs": [
        {
          "key": "out",
          "label": "Out",
          "type": "content"
        }
      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Focus-Scoped Execution\n\n- Only the focused fragment runs scripts, hooks, and live behavior.\n- Nearby fragments may render, but stay dormant.\n- Authority moves with navigation, not with visibility alone.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "isRoot": false,
        "root": false
      }
    },
    {
